              "children": {
                "14": {
                  "id": "14",
                  "speaker": "Gale",
                  "text": "Thrall? No, I think you're mistaken. The name's Gale of Waterdeep. A pleasure to make your acquaintance.",
                  "context": "NodeContext: Projecting. Atop a huge brain floating high above the city, battles raging throughout. Defiant and unfazed in the face of death. Line is a callback to how he first introduces himself",
