      "link": "22",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "20": {
          "id": "20",
          "speaker": "Gale",
          "text": "At least, victory in which we live to tell the tale.",
          "context": "NodeContext: Projecting some, but still speaking in a heartfelt manner to a comrade. Atop a huge brain floating high above the city, battles raging throughout. Referring to the orb - he can destroy the brain, but the party will die",
