                    "18": {
                      "id": "18",
                      "speaker": "Gale",
                      "text": "It has. And a pleasure, a privilege, a tale for the ages, and if I'm being honest... the very best time I've had in my entire life.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: Sincere, lots of camaraderie. Projecting some, but still speaking in a heartfelt manner to a comrade. Atop a huge brain floating high above the city, battles raging throughout.",
